Precision : Out of all the positive prediction we made how many of them were actually true. 
"When I say it's positive, how often am I right?"
 Out of all the people you diagnosed as sick, how many actually have the disease?
 
 
Recall : Out of all the correct answers how many of them are actually inclded in the predicted true section sensitivity or true positive rate. 
 Out of all the people who actually have the disease, how many did you correctly identify?
 
 
F1 Score : combines precision and recall and balances to metrics .
 It's high only when both precision and recall are good.
